data.description: Step into your new, cozy haven! This inviting 3-bedroom, 1-bath home combines charm and practicality for a comfortable living experience. Set on a level lot with a fenced yard, it's the ideal place to unwind while still being within arm's reach of the amenities you crave. An open kitchen and dining area welcomes you with ample natural light and a warm ambiance, perfect for intimate gatherings or relaxed evenings at home. The kitchen offers a user-friendly layout and plenty of cabinet space, catering to your culinary aspirations. With a fenced yard, you can enjoy outdoor activities, keep your pets safe, and cultivate a garden oasis. You'll appreciate the home's proximity to a variety of restaurants, shops, and local attractions. Whether dining out or picking up essentials, everything is nearby. The level lot not only enhances the property's aesthetics but also provides easy access for various outdoor activities. This charming, cozy home suits first-time buyers, small families, or anyone seeking a peaceful retreat with urban convenience. Don't miss the chance to transform this house into your home. Schedule a viewing today and discover the comfort and convenience that awaits you!
